dmca.title: Rotterdam Ska Jazz Foundation complains of a riff on its metatags
dmca.body:
Assen, 10 August, 2006

Dear Google,

I am a member of a Dutch music group called the Rotterdam Ska-Jazz Foundation. We expose ourselves via http://www.rsjf.nl of which I am the owner. I hereby like to file the following notice of infringement.

1. The copyrighted work at issue mainly concerns the meta content text that appears in the index.html file of our website http://www.rsjf.nl. A sample of what one finds when searching Google with the search string
